{"tid":2477230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Android 侵權案：美國最高法院判Google勝訴、甲骨文敗訴","createTime":"2021-04-06T06:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T02:57:14.000Z","uid":131792,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"395ed229e07d2b89ffdf0baf61bf257d6000c052","tid":2477230,"uid":131792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"美國最高法院對甲骨文公司(Oracle Co., ORCL)起訴Google Android智能手機操作系統源代碼侵權案做出了支持Google的裁決，這可能會削弱對軟體版權的保護，但也會讓開發人員有更大空間在彼此產品的基礎上構建產品。Google是Alphabet Inc.(GOOG)旗下公司，此前甲骨文在此案中向Google索賠數十億美元。<br />\n<br />\nWSJ: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/cn.wsj.com/amp/articles/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%259C%25A8Google%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2594%25B2%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259AGoogle%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-11617665710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2F%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E9%2525AB%252598%2525E6%2525B3%252595%2525E9%252599%2525A2%2525E5%25259C%2525A8Google%2525E8%252588%252587%2525E7%252594%2525B2%2525E9%2525AA%2525A8%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E4%2525BE%2525B5%2525E6%2525AC%25258A%2525E6%2525A1%252588%2525E4%2525B8%2525AD%2525E8%2525A3%252581%2525E5%2525AE%25259AGoogle%2525E5%25258B%25259D%2525E8%2525A8%2525B4-11617665710&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4f7d5380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/cn.wsj.com/amp/articles/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%259C%25A8Google%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%2594%25B2%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259AGoogle%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-11617665710</a>"},{"pid":"b314453e1b22b4145c6119adae9ed7cccdeded57","tid":247